descriptionHtml:
Test

async () => {
  await (await _sidebar.default.init(page)).selectJetpack();
  const jetpackPage = await _jetpack.default.init(page);

  expect(await jetpackPage.isConnectBannerVisible()).toBeTruthy();
};
